Author: dawie
Content:
I have a startup (A) that is about to launch a product. I am the only founder. I have 2 friends that have a brilliant idea for a startup (B) and they are going to start working on it soon. They think my startup is an ok idea. They want 20% each of my startup (A) [I have to give up 40%] and they will give me 20% of their new startup(B)

Is this a fair deal?
